| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0498 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 55587b8b-c7f7-5f6d-a43b-f6f995e3c96e"
